# 從頭再嚟
(pos:動詞片語)
<explanation>
yue:重新開始做某件事，通常指喺失敗或挫折之後，由最初嘅步驟再做起（量詞：次）
eng:to start over; to begin again from scratch
<eg>
yue:雖然今次考試考得唔好，但係唔使灰心，下次由頭再嚟就得㗎喇。 (soeng1 ci3 gam3 ci6 haau6 si6 kaau2 dak1 m4 hou2, daan6 si6 m4 syut3 wai1 sam1, haai6 ci6 jau4 tau4 zoi6 lei4 zau6 dak1 gaa3 laa1.)
eng:Although I didn't do well in this exam, there's no need to be discouraged; just start over next time. [end of text]


